Package: accr
Type: Package
Title: Analyzing Accelerometer Data for Small Animal Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Anne", "Aulsebrook", , "anne.aulsebrook@bi.mpg.de", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9217-7043")), 
    person("Mihai", "Valcu", , "mvalcu@gwdg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6907-7802")) )
Description: A toolkit for analyzing accelerometer data from small animal studies. 
    The package provides a range of functions and methods to process, visualize, and extract meaningful information from raw acceleration signals and ODBA (Overall Dynamic Body Acceleration) collected from animal-borne accelerometers. 
